NL**1: :sunglasses: Be cool_ kind_ and civil!**
NL     - It's okay to have opinions and to express them plainly_ but try to be nice about it. If an Admin/Moderator asks you to do something_ please do so. We are here to help.
NL
NL**2. :unamused: Do not @ping or direct message [DM] the Minecraft Staff with unsolicited messages.**

NL     - Helen_ MonsieurV3rt_ Moesh_ Matt and TheRaddestBro have bravely opted out of this rule.
NL
NL**3. :thumbsdown: The following is 100% prohibited:**
NL     a - harassment/abuse of other members
NL     b - racism_ sexism_ sexually explicit or otherwise offensive content_ politics/religion
NL     c - links and/or discussion related to pirated or otherwise illegal content
NL     d - sharing personal or confidential information about another user
NL     e - spam_ self promotion_ advertising other communities/services via direct message or chat
NL      f - using @ everyone or @ here
NL     g - public squabbling - please resolve your issues privately
NL     h - excessive use of special characters in nickname
NL
NL**:scissors: Conduct deemed non compliant with these rules will be removed and action will be taken at the admin/moderators discretion.**
NL

NL*If you feel as though you've witnessed conduct that violates these guidelines_ please send a direct message to an available admin or moderator. If none are online to respond_ or the situation requires immediate intervention_ you can reach us via @ Admin or @ Moderators. Avoid engaging in an arguement over violations.*
